room_title: Escape room "Escape the Haunted Room" by Escape Savannah in Savannah
room_description: You and your friends are on a weekend getaway to Savannah, Georgia. While visiting, your group decides to visit the home of Miss Charlotte Ann Pemberton, once entering the home, you notice the pocket doors to the parlor are slightly ajar. Your group decides to see what secrets the parlor holds to the life and death of Miss Charlotte Ann...
